plot: An entertaining journey across a country that made a business out of a novel: Transylvania, the origin of Bram Stoker's Dracula and ancient home of all vampires, is also characterized by the Transylvania's Saxons, who have been living there for nearly a 1.000 years - until their history came to an end in only one summer in 1990.
title: Die Wahrheit über Dracula
